turbo.domain.UserId.toText.doc =
  {{
  {{ docExample 1 do userId -> turbo.domain.UserId.toText userId }} returns the
  raw text inside `userId`. For example:
  
  ```
  turbo.domain.UserId.toText (turbo.domain.UserId.fromText "alice")
  ```
  
  **Also see:** {{ docLink (docEmbedTermLink do turbo.domain.directChannelKey)
  }}
  }}

